    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread your <strong>warmed tortilla wraps</strong> with some of the <strong>sumac yoghurt</strong>, then add the <strong>quick-pickled salad</strong>, <strong>halved tomato rounds </strong>and 2 <strong>beef kofte</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>cooked onion</strong>,<strong> </strong>any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sumac yoghurt </strong>and your <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
